			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">As far as I can tell, there is a residual aggro or see invis code placed on the mob you charmed.  So after you zone / gate and return, the mob will attack you even if you are invis.  From my experience, it could be either or it could be both.  There have been times when I was well outside the aggro range and the mob came charging after me (indicated residual aggro) and other times when I have been running invis by a pet that someone else had charmed and was attacked.<br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=653282" target=_blank>Sage Casala, Arch Convoker of Saryrn</a>
<br />
Officer | Raid Leader <Familjen></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
			</tr>
