				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">As far as i've noticed, the only time our ex-pets gain the ability to see invis is when the charm is broken with invis... if your charm breaks and you get away, i've never had it see invis.  If it breaks and u die, same thing.  If you zone or gate while it's still your pet, still nothing.  It's when i do something like take the portal in DS to the courtyard and then invis... when i come back to DS, even if not agro on me, conning him while invis still nets a "ready to attack" con.  Just my experience.<br />_________________<br />Komie Nys`T <Anthem>
